column4: The import program will only process the lines having a valid date in column C
It expects columns A, B, D, E to be Sample #, Date, Time and Concentration respectively
It expects columns F through N to have a valid header (on the line that has "Date" in columns C)
Valid headers are:   A280, A260, 260/280, 260/230, Location, Box, Position, Method, Notes
If the column Method is used, it must contain valid medgis codes for the method field
